{"tid":2092714,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（買定離手）六大國安包青天係邊6位？","createTime":"2020-07-03T11:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T11:08:04.000Z","uid":361143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"464871397ed694bf2235239e0dabc73336d6768f","tid":2092714,"uid":361143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:00:19.000Z","msg":"政府今宣佈港區國安委成立，除任命劉賜蕙掌警隊國安部外，特首林鄭亦在徵詢港區國安委和終審法院首席法官的意見後，<span style=\"color: red;\">從現任裁判官中指定6名裁判官為指定法官，</span>負責處理危害國家安全犯罪案件，但未有披露有關法官身份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前已知1個係落埋場踢波既蘇惠德<br />\n<br />\n仲有邊d?<br />\n<br />\n我買<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1，杜浩成<br />\n2，香淑嫻<br />\n3，蘇文隆<br />\n4，吳重儀<br />\n5，陳慧敏"},{"pid":"cc452bf4346c9891da266566d1531263351ff50e","tid":2092714,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"國安六君子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}